snippet.title: A Taste of the Past
snippet.description:
Find our game at https://volcanogirl.itch.io/a-taste-of-the-past made for Ludum Dare 48.

Art by Julia Lee (https://www.instagram.com/artsjulys), Isabelle Szeto (https://twitter.com/eggqty), and Jaimi Qiu (https://twitter.com/owldreig)
Music by Caio Jiacomini (https://twitter.com/caiojmini)

Find more of our games at https://twitter.com/sonderingstudio
